INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,1,'<<Saul was there.>> And he approved of the actions of the men who murdered. Title: The church is treated cruelly. <<Then trouble began.>> That day people treated cruelly the church that were in Jerusalem. All of those believers left Jerusalem and went to other places that were in Judea and Samaria. Only the twelve apostles stayed in Jerusalem.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,2,'<<After was murdered by people,>> some men who worshiped God buried. And they mourned for greatly.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,3,'At that time Saul started treating the church very cruelly to destroy it. He went to many houses to arrest men <<who followed Jesus>> and women <<who followed him>>. And he put those people in prisons.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,4,'Title: Philip goes to Samaria. The believers who left Jerusalem went to many different places. And they preached about Jesus to people.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,5,'<<One of those believers was Philip.>> Philip went to a city that was in Samaria. And he told people who were in Samaria that Jesus was the Christ.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,6,'The crowds heard Philip and saw the miracles that he performed by using God''s power. So the crowds listened carefully to all of the words that Philip said.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,7,'For evil spirits who controlled people shouted loudly when they were sent from many people. And many lame people and many people who weren''t able to move their bodies were healed.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,8,'So many people who were in the city rejoiced.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,9,'Title: Simon believes the message Philip. <<A man named>> Simon used magic in that city for many years. And because of the things that Simon did, all of the people Samaria were amazed. Simon proudly often said that he was a great person.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,10,'All of the ordinary people and all of the important people listened to Simon carefully. And those people said, This man has great power because God causes him to be great.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,11,'Those people followed Simon because he amazed them for many years by using magic.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,12,'But Philip preached to people the good news that was about God''s kingdom. And he preached to people that Jesus was the Christ. And when the men and the women believed the message Philip, they were dipped in water.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,13,'Simon also believed the message Philip and was dipped in water. Then he started following Philip continuously. And because of the miracles that Simon saw Philip performing through God''s power, he was continuously amazed.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,14,'The men that Jesus sent to people so that they would be his representatives for people were in Jerusalem. And after those apostles heard that many people <<the province named>> Samaria believed God''s message <<that was about Jesus>>, they sent Peter and John to them.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,15,'After Peter and John arrived in Samaria, they prayed for those believers so that they would receive the Holy Spirit.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,16,'For the Holy Spirit didn''t come to the Christians yet. Literal Alternate: Those believers were baptized in water in the name the Lord named Jesus. Dynamic Alternate: <<Earlier>> they were baptized in water by Philip because they believed in the Lord named Jesus. End of Alternates. <<But a person didn''t pray for those believers yet so that they would receive the Holy Spirit.>>');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,17,'Then Peter and John put Peter''s and John''s hands on the Christians. And those believers received the Holy Spirit.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,18,'Simon saw that after the men that Jesus sent to people so that they would be his representatives for people put the hands of the men that he sent to them so that they would be his representatives for people on those people, they received the Holy Spirit. So Simon offered money to the apostles.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,19,'And Simon said, Cause me to become powerful so that each person that I put my hands on would receive the Holy Spirit.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,20,'Peter said, May your money be destroyed. And may you be destroyed. For you thought that you were able to buy God''s for money!');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,21,'Literal Alternate: You have no part of this work. Dynamic Alternate: You''re not able to work with us. End of Alternates. For God knows that you''re thinking badly.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,22,'Repent. Turn away from that evil thought and pray to the Lord. Perhaps the Lord will forgive you for this thought that is in your heart.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,23,'For I very much know that you want the things that we have and that you sin continuously like <<an evil master''s>> slave <<does>> evil things.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,24,'Then Simon said, Pray to the Lord for me so that the things that you said wouldn''t happen to me.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,25,'After Peter and John told the people <<who were in Samaria>> the things that they knew <<and were <<about Jesus>>>>, and after they preached God''s message to the people <<who were in there>>, they started returning to Jerusalem. They preached to <<many>> people in many villages Samaria the gospel <<that was about Jesus>> while they went to Jerusalem.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,26,'Title: Philip meets a man. Then an angel who came from the Lord said to Philip, Go to the road that leads from Jerusalem to <<the town named>> Gaza the southern desert.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,27,'So Philip started going. While Philip was going <<on the road that led from Jerusalem to Gaza>>, he met a eunuch. That man was from <<the country named>> and was an important official who was responsible for the extremely valuable things of the queen named. That man had gone to Jerusalem to worship God.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,28,'And while that man was returning <<to>>, he was sitting in his chariot. And he was reading the book that the prophet named Isaiah wrote.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,29,'The Spirit told Philip, Go to that chariot and stay near it.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,30,'Then Philip ran to the chariot and heard that man reading the book of the prophet named Isaiah. Philip asked that man, Do you understand the words that you''re reading?');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,31,'That man said, How am I able to understand these words unless a person explains <<their>> meaning to me? So he invited Philip to come up <<into the chariot>> and he sat with him.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,32,'The eunuch was reading the following part of God''s book <<that was about a man>>. That part of God''s book <<said>>, People led this man to kill him like people lead a sheep to kill him. And this man didn''t complain <<while people caused him to suffer>> like a sheep is quiet while a person cuts his wool off.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,33,'This man was insulted and wasn''t treated justly. Who is able to tell people about this man''s descendants? For people killed this man while he was on an earth <<so he never will have descendants>>.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,34,'The eunuch said to Philip, Please answer the question me. About whom does the prophet talk? Does that prophet talk about himself or another person?');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,35,'Then Philip <<started explaining>> the meaning that part of God''s book and told that man the gospel that was about Jesus.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,36,'That eunuch and Philip came to a place that had water while they traveled on that road. And that eunuch said to Philip, Look. A pool of water is here. Please dip me in water unless you know a reason that prevents you from dipping me in it.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,37,'Philip said, If you certainly believe <<that Jesus is the Christ and that he is God''s son>>, I''ll dip you in water. That eunuch said, I believe that Jesus is the Christ and that he is the Son of God. Footnote: This verse isn''t in the manuscripts that people trust the.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,38,'So that eunuch ordered the person who was controlling the chariot to cause it to stop moving. Then Philip and that eunuch went into the water. And Philip dipped that eunuch in water.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,39,'After Philip and that eunuch came up the water, the Holy Spirit the Lord took Philip away <<another place>>. Although that eunuch didn''t see Philip again, he continued going on the road <<that led from Jerusalem to Gaza>>. And he continued being joyful <<because God saved him from the sins him>>.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',8,40,'Then Philip appeared in <<the town named>>. He traveled to many places and preached the gospel in all of the towns that were in that region until he arrived in <<the city named>>.');
