INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,8,'Explained those servants and that soldier the things the things happened to. Then sent those people to Joppa <<so that they would ask Peter to come to>>.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,9,'Title: Peter sees a dream. The next day when those people already were near Joppa, at about noon Peter went up to the roof of the house <<that he was staying>> to pray.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,10,'Peter became hungry and wanted eats some food. While people were preparing Peter''s food, he saw a dream.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,11,'Peter saw that heaven was opened by God. And something that looked like a big sheet was lowered to the earth by God. And the four corners that sheet were held by God.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,12,'That sheet contained all of the kinds of animals that had four feet snakes and wild birds. <<Those animals included them.>>');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,13,'Then God the voice said to Peter, Peter, stand up. Kill some of those animals to eat some of them');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,14,'Peter replied, Lord, I''ll do this! Literal Alternate: I always eat only meat that is and clean religiously. Dynamic Alternate: I always eat only meat that the law allows to eat');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,15,'Then God the voice spoke to Peter a second time. God the voice said, Don''t call a bad thing ''something that God caused became clean religiously''.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,16,'God the voice said those words to Peter three times. And that sheet was returned immediately to heaven by God.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,17,'While Peter was trying to understand the meaning of the dream, the men that sent <<so that they would find him>> learned about the place where Simon''s house was. And they arrived in the Dung Gate that house.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,18,'The men loudly asked, A man that Peter is also called ''~ by people named Simon are staying at this house?');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,19,'While Peter was still thinking about the dream, the Holy Spirit said to him, Three men are searching for you.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,20,'Therefore, stand up and go down the stairs to those men. Don''t refuse to go with those men. For I sent those men to you');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,21,'Peter went down the stairs and said to those men, I''m the man who are searching for. Why did you come to me?');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,22,'The men answered, , was a Roman officer who commanded about one hundred soldiers, sent us to you. Is a good person and honors God. All of the Jews fear. A special servant who came from God told to ask you to come to house. That servant wanted to hear the message that you''ll tell to');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,23,'Then Peter invited the men to enter the house so that they would stay for one night. Title: Peter visits'' house. The next day Peter and the men started traveling to''s house. Some people who believed in Jesus Joppa traveled there with Peter and the men.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,24,'In the next day Peter and those men arrived at. Was waiting for Peter and those men. Had asked family to come to house. <<So''s family and the friends were also waiting for Peter at house.>>');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,25,'When Peter entered the house, met him. And knelt in front of Peter to honor him.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,26,'But Peter helped stand up. He said, Stand up. I''m an only man.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,27,'While Peter was talking to, he entered a big room the house. And he saw many people who were there.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,28,'Peter said to those people, You certainly know that the law doesn''t allow we do certain things. The law doesn''t allow we join people who aren''t Jews. Or we visit them Literal Alternate: But God taught me I''ll say that a person is dirty or bad religiously. Dynamic Alternate: But God taught me he''ll accept a person who isn''t a Jew.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,29,'So when you sent the men you so that they would bring me here, I agreed immediately to come. Please tell me the reason that you sent those men so that they would bring me here');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,30,'Replied, Three days ago I was in my house. I was praying God 3 pm. Suddenly a man who was wearing bright clothes appeared in front of me.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,31,'That man said, , when you prayed to God, he listened and noticed your gifts that you gave to poor people. <<God will help you.>>');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,32,'So send the men you to Joppa now so that they you would bring there him named Simon. That man is a guest at the house of another Simon, who makes things with leather, and who lives near the Dead Sea?');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,33,'So I immediately sent the men me so that they me would bring you to my house. And I thank you because you came. All of us are with God here now to hear about the things that the Lord commanded you to tell us');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,34,'Then Peter started speaking. He said, Now I realize that God treats all of the people fairly.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,35,'And God accepts of each nation people who honor him and who does the things the things please God?');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,36,'You know the message that God sent to Israel''s people. God said to those people that he''ll cause them to have a good relationship with him through Jesus Christ who is a king of all of people again.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,37,'You know about the things that Jesus did in Galilee first. And you know about the things that Jesus did throughout the province Judea. After and after John the Baptist dipped people in in water, he taught they should change into their thoughts and their actions so that they would please God, Jesus started doing those things.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,38,'You know that God chose Jesus Nazareth. And God showed people the Holy Spirit always was with Jesus Nazareth. And he there has his power Jesus went to many different places. In those places Jesus did good things. And Jesus caused people that the chief evil spirit caused suffered to become healthy. Literal Alternate: He was able to do all of these things because God was with him. Dynamic Alternate: Jesus was able to do all of these things because God was always helping him.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,39,'We saw all of the things that Jesus did in Jerusalem and in the Jews'' whole land. The leaders <<that in Jerusalem>> killed Jesus by hanging him on a cross.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,40,'But on the third day God caused Jesus to rise from the dead. And God caused Jesus to be seen by certain people.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,41,'All of the people were able to see Jesus. But previously God chose certain people so that certain they would be able to see Jesus and so that certain they would be able to tell them about him. We are those people who ate food with Jesus and who drank with Jesus? And after Jesus rose from the dead, we did those things.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,42,'Jesus commanded us to tell Jewish people about him. And we tell him to be the person that God chose to be a judge he''ll judge people who will be at the living time when he''ll come to judge them and them.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,43,'Many years ago all of the people who told God''s messages to told them about a Christ. They said that if he believes in a Christ, God will forgive his because of the things that a Christ did bad actions');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,44,'While Peter was still speaking about these words, the Holy Spirit came down on all of the people who were listening to the message him.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,45,'It the Jewish people who believed in Jesus were surprised and that who came from Joppa with Peter? Literal Alternate: For God also poured the Holy Spirit out onto the people who weren''t Jews. Dynamic Alternate: For God also gave the Holy Spirit to the people who weren''t Jews.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,46,'<<Those Jewish people knew that God did that.>> For they were hearing''s family and the friends speaking about strange languages. And they praised God');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,47,'Then Peter said, People should prevent us from dipping them water. These people received the Holy Spirit like we received him');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',10,48,'Literal Alternate: So Peter said that and the friends family should be dipped by a person by in Jesus'' name in water. Dynamic Alternate: So Peter said that and the friends family should be dipped by a person by in water because and the friends they believe in Jesus now. End of Alternates. <<The Jewish people dipped family and the friends in water.>> Then and the friends family asked Peter to stay at house for a few days.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',11,1,'Title: Peter explains the actions him. The leaders that Jesus sent to people so that they would be for people his representatives and they heard that they also believed God''s message <<that him>>. And who was in Judea?');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',11,2,'When Peter went to Jerusalem, the Jewish people opposed him. <<They thought that the skin that was at the end of all of the men who were followers should be cut off by him.>>');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',11,3,'Those Jewish people said to Peter, You went into certain men''s house. The skin that was on the end those men was cut off by a person. And you also ate with those men!');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',11,4,'Peter started explaining those Jewish people all of the things the things happened.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',11,5,'Peter said, I was praying in the city named Joppa and saw a dream. In that dream me saw an object that looked like a big piece a cloth. That object was coming from heaven. The four corners that object were held by God while it was lowered by him. And that object came in front of me.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',11,6,'I looked at that object carefully and saw a farm, animals that had four legs them, them, and wild birds. <<And all of those animals that were on that object were animals that the law us didn''t allow to eat.>>');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',11,7,'Then I heard a voice. That voice said to me, Peter, stand up. Kill some of those animals to eat some of them.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',11,8,'But I replied, Lord, no! I''ll do this! I never ate religiously or bad dirty meat <<that the law us didn''t allow to eat>>.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',11,9,'Then God the voice that came from heaven spoke to me a second time. Literal Alternate: That voice said, Don''t call dirty things religiously ''the things that I caused became clean religiously''. Dynamic Alternate: The voice said, Don''t refuse to accept the things that I caused became clean religiously.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',11,10,'Those words were said to Peter three times by God the voice. And that object was pulled to heaven by God.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',11,11,'And three men who were sent from by arrived immediately at the house that I was staying.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',11,12,'The Holy Spirit told me that I should go with those men <<even though they aren''t Jews>>. These six Jewish Christians also came from Joppa with me. We entered''s house.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',11,13,'Then told us that saw in a dream a servant who came from God and that who appeared in house? And that servant said to, Send some men to Joppa so that Simon, whom ''~ Peter is called by people, would be brought here by some men.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',11,14,'That man will explain God is able to save you and all of the people who are in your house from your bad actions.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',11,15,'After I started speaking to those people, the Holy Spirit came down immediately on them. He came down like he came down first on us on the day that was after a Passover.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',11,16,'Then I remembered the words the Lord. The Lord said, John dipped people in in water. But you''ll be united by God the Holy Spirit.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',11,17,'God also gave those Gentiles the Holy Spirit who was a gift like he gave the Holy Spirit to us <<, whom Jews,>> and who also believed in the Lord, who was Jesus Christ? Should I oppose God?');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',11,18,'After those people heard Peter, they stopped opposing him. And they praised God. Then they said, Now we realize that God has accepted the Gentiles. If those people change into their thoughts and their actions so that they could please God, they''ll also live with him forever.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',11,19,'Title: The Christians tell the gospel to them. After the Jewish leaders <<that in Jerusalem>> killed, many Christians ran away from those Jewish leaders. They ran away to many different places because those Jewish leaders caused them to suffer. Many of them traveled, and named areas to. In those places those people continuously told the message <<Jesus>>. Those people told that message to only Jews.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',11,20,'But some of those people who were from and Cyrene went to. And they started also speaking to them. They told the gospel them the Lord Jesus.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',11,21,'The Lord was greatly helping those people <<boldly told the gospel those Jews who spoke about a Greek him Jesus>>. And very many people became followers the Lord.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',11,22,'A church heard them <<believing in Jesus in>>. And in Jerusalem so a group of those leaders sent Barnabas to.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',11,23,'After Barnabas arrived in, he saw that grace was given to the people by God. Dynamic Alternate: After Barnabas arrived in, he saw that God was very kind to the people. End of Alternates. So Barnabas was happy and encouraged those people to continue completely trusting in the Lord.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',11,24,'Barnabas was a good man. Barnabas was filled by God with the Holy Spirit. Barnabas completely trusted in God. So many people believe in the Lord <<because Barnabas helped them>>.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',11,25,'Then Barnabas went to to search for Saul.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',11,26,'After Barnabas found Saul, he brought Saul to. For whole one year Barnabas and Saul met a church there and taught them about Jesus. Was the place where Christians were called first by them ''the people who followed Jesus''.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',11,27,'<<When Barnabas and Saul were in,>> during that time prophets went from Jerusalem to. <<And who believed in Jesus?>>');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',11,28,'Of those one people named stood up <<to speak to the followers>>. The Holy Spirit told a message to and caused to tell it to the followers. Said, Very many people will suffer soon because there will be it in many countries. When was the ruler, that thing happened.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',11,29,'So the followers <<that in>> decided to send money to help whom them and live in Judea? They gave the amount of money that they were able to give.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Acts',11,30,'And those followers gave the money and Saul to Barnabas. Barnabas and Saul took that gift to the elders of the group that was in Jerusalem.');
