INSERT INTO English VALUES('Philemon',1,1,'');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Philemon',1,2,'We are also writing this letter to Apphia, who also believes in Jesus Christ, and Archippus, who also struggles for Jesus Christ with us. And we are also writing this letter to the other people who worship God in your house.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Philemon',1,3,'We pray that God, who is our Father, and Jesus Christ, who is our Lord, will treat you kindly. And we pray that God and Jesus Christ will cause you to be peaceful.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Philemon',1,4,'Title: Paul thanks God because of Philemon and he prays for Philemon. I worship God. And when I pray to God for you, I thank him because of you.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Philemon',1,5,'I thank God because I heard good news that is about you. I heard that you continue trusting in the Lord Jesus. And I heard that you continue loving God and his special people.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Philemon',1,6,'I pray that God will teach you about all of the good things that he has given to us. And I pray that God will unite you with other Christians. I pray that these things will happen so that people would honor Christ.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Philemon',1,7,'Friend, you love God and other people and bless his special people. These things bless me. And these things help me trust in God.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Philemon',1,8,'Title: Paul asks Philemon to accept Onesimus. I want you to do a certain thing. And you should do this. I''m able to command you to do this because Christ has given authority to me.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Philemon',1,9,'But we love each other. And I''m old now and in this prison because I serve Jesus Christ. So I''ll ask you to do this.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Philemon',1,10,'I''m asking you to welcome Onesimus. While I was in this prison, I helped Onesimus believe in Jesus Christ. So Onesimus is like my child. Footnote: Onesimus was a slave who belonged to Philemon. But Onesimus left Philemon.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Philemon',1,11,'Previously Onesimus didn''t help you. But recently Onesimus helped me. And Onesimus is able to help you. Footnote: Onesimus'' name means a person who helps people.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Philemon',1,12,'So I''m sending Onesimus to you even though I love him a lot.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Philemon',1,13,'I want Onesimus to stay with me. I''m in this prison because I tell God''s good message to people. And if Onesimus were to stay with me, he would be able to help me for you.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Philemon',1,14,'But I don''t want Onesimus to stay with me unless you allow him to stay with me. I don''t want to force you to help me. Instead, I want you to do good things because you want to do them.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Philemon',1,15,'Perhaps Onesimus was not with you for a short time so that he could be with you again forever.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Philemon',1,16,'Then Onesimus won''t be only your slave. Instead, Onesimus will be your friend, who also believes in Jesus Christ. I love Onesimus a lot. But you should love Onesimus more than I. You''ll love Onesimus because he is your faithful slave. But you''ll also love Onesimus because he is united by God with the Lord.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Philemon',1,17,'So welcome Onesimus because you and I serve God. Welcome Onesimus like you welcome me.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Philemon',1,18,'If Onesimus did a bad thing to you, I''ll pay money to you. If Onesimus owes money to you, I''ll pay it to you.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Philemon',1,19,'I''m writing this part of this letter with my hand. If Onesimus owes money to you, I''ll pay it to you. But remember that you owe your life to me. You''ll live with God forever because I helped you believe in Jesus Christ.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Philemon',1,20,'Friend, I want you to welcome Onesimus. We are united by God with the Lord. So welcome Onesimus. Then you''ll bless me.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Philemon',1,21,'I have asked you to welcome Onesimus. While I''m writing this letter to you, I know that you''ll do this. And I know that you''ll do more good things.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Philemon',1,22,'Title: Other people greet Philemon. Please also prepare a room so that I could stay there. I hope that God will cause me to return to you because you''re praying for me.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Philemon',1,23,'Epaphras also is in this prison with me because he serves Jesus Christ. Epaphras greets you.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Philemon',1,24,'Mark, Aristarchus, Demas, and Luke serve God with me. They also greet you.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Philemon',1,25,'I pray that Jesus Christ, who is our Lord, will treat you kindly.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',1,1,'We are Paul and Timothy. We are the servants of Jesus Christ. We are writing this letter and are sending it to all of you who are God''s holy people in Philippi. You''re in Jesus Christ. We are also sending this letter to your leaders and your deacons.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',1,2,'May God, who is our Father, and the Lord Jesus Christ give grace and peace to you.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',1,3,'Whenever I think about you, I thank my God.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',1,4,'And whenever I pray for you, I pray very joyfully.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',1,5,'I''m happy because you joined me to tell the good news to other people. You helped me from the first day until now.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',1,6,'God started doing a good work in you. And I know that God will continue doing a good work in you until he finishes doing that work on the day when Jesus Christ returns.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',1,7,'It is right that I think these things about all of you. I love you with all of my heart. Sometimes I''m in chains and sometimes am defending the truth of the good news. But all of you always share God''s grace with me.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',1,8,'God knows that I want to be with all of you. I earnestly want to be with you because Jesus Christ caused me to love you like Jesus Christ loves you.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',1,9,'I pray that your love will grow abundantly. And I pray that you''ll love more because you know things and because you understand things.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',1,10,'Then you''ll be able to choose the things that are best. And you''ll become pure and blameless on the day when Christ will return.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',1,11,'You''ll be filled with the fruit of righteousness that Jesus Christ gives to people. All of these things cause God to be glorified. And all of these things cause God to be praised.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',1,12,'Brothers and sisters, I want you to know that all of the bad things that people did to me caused more people to hear about the gospel.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',1,13,'I certainly know that I''m in chains because I tell other people about Christ. All of the palace guards and all of the other people who are here know this.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',1,14,'And most of the brothers and the sisters have become braver for the Lord because I''m in chains. They bravely proclaim the good news now. And they aren''t afraid.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',1,15,'It is true that some people preach about Christ because they are jealous. But other people preach about Christ to help me do my work.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',1,16,'The second group of people do those things because they love me. They know that I was put in this prison to tell other people about the good news.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',1,17,'But those other people preach about Christ because they want to become more important than me. They preach about Christ because of wrong motives. They think that while I''m in chains, they are causing me to have trouble.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',1,18,'But I don''t care about those things. Whenever people tell other people about Christ, I''m always happy. When people who have good reasons for telling the gospel to people are telling people about Christ, I''m happy. And when people who have bad reasons for telling the gospel to people are telling people about Christ, I also am happy. And I will continue being happy.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',1,19,'And I will continue rejoicing because I know that God will answer your prayers. And I know that the Holy Spirit of Jesus Christ will help me. And I know that the Holy Spirit of Jesus Christ will cause the rulers to release me from this prison.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',1,20,'I completely expect not to be ashamed. And I hope that I won''t be ashamed. I certainly know that I''ll be brave. Because of the things that happen to me, Christ will always receive glory. Whether I live, or I die, Christ will receive glory.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',1,21,'The reason why I live is Christ. But if I die, I''ll gain good things.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',1,22,'If I continue living in my body, I''ll be able to continue doing my work. And my work will produce a lot of fruit. But which choice should I choose? I don''t know the thing that I should choose!');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',1,23,'It is difficult for me to decide. Sometimes I want to leave this earth. Then I''ll be with Christ. If I were to stay on this earth here, I would be happy. If I were to go to heaven to be with Christ, I would be extremely happy.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',2,1,'But it is more important for you that I continue living.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',2,2,'I certainly know that this is true. So I know that I''ll stay with you. And I will continue working with all of you to help your faith grow. I''ll continue also helping you learn things so that you could rejoice.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',2,3,'I certainly know that I''ll be with you again. Then you''ll be able to boast about Jesus Christ because of me more.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',2,4,'Whether good things happen to you, or bad things happen to you, always live so that your lives could honor the good news that is about Christ. Then I''ll know that you still are strong in the one Spirit. Whether I come to see you, or I hear about you, I''ll know that you still are strong. And I will know that you work with each other like one person works. And I will know that you work to teach other people about the good news.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',2,5,'So don''t be afraid of those people who oppose you. When you aren''t afraid of those people, they''ll know that they''ll be destroyed and that you''ll be saved. God will do these things.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',2,6,'God gave you certain things that you have to do for Christ. You have to believe in Christ first. But you have to also suffer for Christ.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',2,7,'You''re struggling like I''m struggling. You saw me struggling. And recently you heard that I''m still struggling.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',2,8,'Title: Paul''s prayer. Therefore if you were encouraged by Christ, or if he comforted you, or if you have a relationship with the Spirit, or if he was merciful to you,');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',2,9,'Agree with each other and love each other with the same kind of love. When you think, and when you act, be like one spirit. You''ll cause me to rejoice by doing these things.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',2,10,'Don''t do things to become more important than other people. And don''t do things because you''re proud. Instead, be humble. Think that those other people are more important than you.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',2,11,'Don''t care only about your life. But also care about other people''s lives.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',2,12,'Think like Jesus Christ thought.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',2,13,'Jesus Christ completely was God. But Jesus Christ didn''t keep God''s power or his rights.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',2,14,'Instead, Jesus left his rights and his power. He did this by becoming a servant. Jesus became a human.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',2,15,'Jesus looked like a man. And Jesus was humble. He completely obeyed God. Although these things caused Jesus to die, he did them. He died on a cross!');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',2,16,'So God lifted Jesus to the highest place and gave him the name that is more important than all other names.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',2,17,'When Jesus'' name is said, all people and all angels will kneel to worship him. All of the people and all of the angels who are in heaven, on the earth, and under the earth will kneel to worship Jesus.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',2,18,'All people and all angels will say that Jesus Christ is Lord. And God the Father will receive the glory.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',2,19,'My friends that I love, you have always obeyed God. You obeyed God while I was with you. And you have obeyed God more while I''m not with you. So continue working out your salvation. And while you''re working out your salvation, you should be afraid.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',2,20,'God helps you want to do the things that please him. And he helps you do the things that please him.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',2,21,'When you do things, don''t complain. And don''t argue.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',2,22,'Then no person will accuse you of doing bad things. And you''ll become very good. You''re God''s children. And while you''re living among people who always do evil things, you''ll become very good. While you''re teaching those people how to be able to live forever, they''ll see that you''re good. And they''ll see that you''re good like people see bright stars that shine in the dark heavens.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',3,1,'You''ll shine while you hold the word of life tightly. Then I''ll be able to boast about you on the day when Christ returns. That day I''ll be happy because I didn''t run without a reason and because I didn''t work without a reason.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',3,2,'But perhaps my life will be poured out on your sacrifices like the priests pour a drink offering out on people''s sacrifices. I know that you serve God because you believe in Jesus. So I''m glad and rejoice with all of you.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',3,3,'So you also should be happy and rejoice with me.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',3,4,'Title: Paul wants to send Timothy and Epaphroditus to the Christians who are in Philippi. I hope that the Lord Jesus will allow me to send Timothy to you soon. When Timothy visits you, you''ll be happy. And when Timothy brings to me news that is about you, I''ll be happy.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',3,5,'I don''t know another person who is like Timothy. Timothy will truly care about you.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',3,6,'Other people care about only the things that they want. They don''t care about the things that Jesus Christ wants.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',3,7,'But you know that Timothy is a good person. Timothy served God with me to preach the gospel like a child serves his father.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',3,8,'So after I hear about the things that will happen to me, I hope to send Timothy to you.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',3,9,'And if the Lord allows me to come to you, I certainly know that I''ll come to you soon.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',3,10,'You sent Epaphroditus to me so that he could bring a message to me. And when I needed a person to help me, you sent Epaphroditus to me to take care of me. Epaphroditus is in God''s family and worked with me. And Epaphroditus struggled with me like a soldier struggles to fight an enemy. But I think that I should send Epaphroditus to you.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',3,11,'Epaphroditus longs to be with all of you. He is troubled because you heard that he was sick.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',3,12,'It is true that Epaphroditus was very sick. And Epaphroditus almost died. But God was merciful to Epaphroditus and also merciful to me. If Epaphroditus had died, I would have been very sad. But God allowed Epaphroditus to live.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',3,13,'So I really want to send Epaphroditus to you. Then when you see Epaphroditus again, you''ll be glad. And I will worry less.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',3,14,'So welcome Epaphroditus joyfully like you welcome a brother who trusts in the Lord. Honor people who are like Epaphroditus.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',3,15,'While Epaphroditus was working for Christ, he almost died. So we should honor Epaphroditus because he worked for Christ. Epaphroditus helped me for you. When you were not able to help me because you were not with me, Epaphroditus helped me.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',3,16,'Title: Christ is more important than all other things. Now I want to write about other things. My friends, rejoice because you belong to the Lord. It isn''t difficult for me to write to you about the same things that earlier I wrote about to you. These things will help you be safe.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',3,17,'There are dangerous people who want to cut your bodies. They are Jews who want all Christians to obey all the laws of Moses. And they want each male Christian to be circumcised. The things that those people are doing are evil. So when you''re with those people, be careful.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',3,18,'We are the people who truly are God''s people. We serve God through his Holy Spirit. And we are proud of only Jesus Christ. We don''t trust in ourselves.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',3,19,'I have many reasons so that I could trust in myself and the things that I did. Other people might think that they have reasons so that they could trust in those things. But I have more reasons.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',3,20,'When I was eight days old, I was circumcised. I''m Israel''s descendant and am in the tribe of Benjamin. I''m a true Hebrew. And my parents also were true Hebrews. I was a Pharisee and obeyed the law of Moses carefully.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',3,21,'I persecuted the church because I wanted to please God. I attacked the church. I obeyed the law perfectly.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',4,1,'Before I trusted in Christ, I thought that those things were valuable. But now I think because of Christ that those things aren''t valuable.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',4,2,'It is extremely great that I know Christ Jesus, who is my Lord. And when I think about knowing Christ, no other things seem to be valuable. I left all of those other things for Christ. I think that all of those other things are garbage so that I could know Christ more.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',4,3,'I want God to unite me with Christ. And I want God to think that I''m righteous. But God won''t think that I''m righteous because I obey the law of Moses. I want to trust in Christ. Then God will think that I''m righteous because I trust in Christ.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',4,4,'I want to know Christ better. And I want to know about the power that caused Christ to rise from the dead. I want to join Christ by suffering with him. And I want to become like Christ by dying with him.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',4,5,'I want all of these things so that after I die, God would cause me to become alive again.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',4,6,'I didn''t receive all of these things yet and didn''t reach my goal yet. But Christ Jesus is holding me so that I could reach that goal. So I work hard continuously to reach that goal.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',4,7,'Brothers and sisters, I don''t think that I already reached the goal. But I always do one thing. I forget about the things that are behind me. And I work hard to obtain the things that are in front of me.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',4,8,'I run hard toward that goal to win the prize. God appointed me to win that prize. The prize that is in heaven is Christ Jesus.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',4,9,'Primary: All of you who are mature should think about these things like I think about them. Alternate 1: All of you who are like Christ should think about these things like I think about them. Alternate 2: All of you who have learned all the things that you should learn should think about these things like I think about them. End of Alternates. And if you don''t think about these things correctly, God will help you think correctly.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',4,10,'But let''s live now like Christ expects us to live.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',4,11,'Friends, do the things that I did when I was with you. And watch carefully the people who live like we live.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',4,12,'Many people oppose the things that Christ did when he died on the cross. But they say that they believe in Christ. I already told you about those people many times. And when I think about those people, I cry.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',4,13,'Those people will be destroyed by God. They care the most about the food that they eat. And they are proud of certain things that they did. But they should be ashamed of those things. They think about only things that are on the earth.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',4,14,'But our country is heaven. And we are eagerly waiting for Lord Jesus, who is the Savior, to come from heaven to us.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',4,15,'Jesus has the power to control all things. He''ll change with his power our bodies that we have on earth. Then our bodies will become like Jesus'' glorious body.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',4,16,'Title: God wants you to do certain things. My friends, I love you and want to be with you. You bless me. And I''m proud of you because you follow the Lord. So continue following the Lord.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',4,1,'I plead with Euodia and Syntyche to agree with each other because you belong to the Lord.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',4,18,'My true friend, I''m asking you to do one thing. Help those women because they served God with me. Those women worked with me to tell the good news to other people. And Clement and the other people who worked with me also told the good news to other people. All of those people''s names were written in the Book of Life.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',4,19,'Always rejoice because you belong to the Lord. I''ll say this command again. Rejoice!');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',4,20,'Show all people that you''re gentle. The Lord will return to the earth soon.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',4,21,'Don''t worry about things. But pray to God and ask him to give you all the things that you need. And when you pray to God, always thank him because he did many great things for you.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',4,22,'Then God''s peace will protect your hearts and your minds. God will do these things because you belong to Christ Jesus. We''ll never be able to completely understand God''s peace.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',4,23,'So friends, continue thinking about things that are true, things that God respects, things that are right, things that are pure, things that are beautiful, things that he admires, things that are extremely good, and things that he praises.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',4,24,'Do all of the things that you learned from me. And do all of the things that you received from me. And do all of the things that you heard me saying. Follow my example. Then God, who gives peace to us, will be with you.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',4,25,'I rejoice because I belong to the Lord. And I thank the Lord because you care about me again. Previously you cared about me. But previously you were not able to show me that you cared about me.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',4,26,'I don''t need you to send more things to me. I learned how to be content with the things that I have. And I learned how to be content with the things that happen to me.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',4,27,'At certain times I didn''t have things that I needed. And at other times I had more things than I needed. But I learned how to be content. When good things happen to me, and when bad things happen to me, I''m content. When I''m full, and when I''m hungry, I''m content. When I have enough things, and when I don''t have enough things, I''m content.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',4,28,'I''m able to do all of these things by Christ''s power. Christ gives strength to me.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',4,29,'But when I had trouble, it was good that you helped me.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',4,30,'And you who believe in Jesus at Philippi know about the things that happened when I left Macedonia. No churches helped me by giving things to me. You were the only people who helped me. After you heard about the good news first, you helped me.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',4,31,'And when I was in Thessalonica, you sent to me several times the things that I needed.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',4,32,'I don''t want you to give more things to me now. But after you give things to me, I want you to receive the good things that God will give to you.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',5,1,'I have all the things that I need. Actually I don''t need all the things that I have. Epaphroditus brought to me the things that you sent to me. So I have now all of the things that I need. The things that you gave to me are like a sacrifice that you offered to God. And God accepts that sacrifice that you offered to him. And that sacrifice pleases God.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',5,2,'My God will provide all of the things that you need. He is able to provide all of those things because he is extremely rich. Those good things will come to you because you belong to Christ Jesus.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',5,3,'I glorify our God, who is our Father, greatly.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',5,4,'Greet all of God''s saints. Those people belong to Christ Jesus. The brothers and sisters who are with me greet you.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',5,5,'All of God''s saints who are here greet you. And the people who live in Caesar''s palace also greet you.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Ephesians',5,6,'May the grace of the Lord Jesus Christ be with your spirit. Amen.');
