INSERT INTO English VALUES('Proverbs',20,28,'It a king who loves his people and the LORD will be safe and that who is faithful to them? Literal Alternate: That king''s chair will be safe because he loves his people and the LORD. Dynamic Alternate: That king will continue ruling by loving his people and the LORD. End of Alternates. Footnote: ''or this verse'' might mean, ''a king will be safe because the LORD loves him and because he is faithful to a king''.');
