INSERT INTO English VALUES('Proverbs',21,4,'Literal Alternate: Evil people have proud eyes and proud hearts. Dynamic Alternate: They are proud. End of Alternates. Those people''s thoughts are like a lamp that leads them so that they could do bad things. Footnote: ''or this verse'' might mean, ''evil people are like dirt that weeds grow because they are proud''. Those people''s proud thoughts cause them to do bad things.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Proverbs',21,5,'The plans that a person who works hard makes will cause him to get all of the things that he needs. But a person who acts quickly <<and doesn''t plan the things that he''ll do>> will become poor.');
INSERT INTO English VALUES('Proverbs',21,6,'Literal Alternate: Wealth that a person gets because he has a tongue that lies won''t stay. Dynamic Alternate: A person who gets wealth by lying won''t continue having it. End of Alternates. That wealth is like a cloud that people will stop being able to see quickly. Literal Alternate: And people who try to get that wealth <<by lying>> will get death. Dynamic Alternate: And people who try to get that wealth <<by lying>> will die.');
